      "input": "Content: LabName: Hostname field of the \"System Info\" table on the dashboard page.\n\nIpAddress: IP Address field of the \"System Info\" table on the dashboard page.\n\nTicket Template\nOpen the Service Management application and create a new ticket with IT. In the search box type \"f5\" and a submenu appears where you will choose \"Vanity URL Requests F5\".\n\nShort Description: PegaLabs -- Create Internal Vanity URL\n\nDetailed Description: Please create vanity URL https://<LabName>.lab.pega.com --> https://<IpAddress>:8443/ using the *.lab.pega.com certificate.\n\nFill out the additional fields as follows replacing <LAB NAME> and <LAB IP Address> with the values from above.\n\nNOTE: Once the request is completed by the NetOps Team, you should be able to access the system using the vanity URL."
